      "title": "56 people injured in the protest are in hospital",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "56 people who were injured during the demonstration yesterday (09) near the Colombo Fort Presidential Palace are still receiving treatment at the Colombo National Hospital.",
        "One of them is being treated in the emergency department. Among the injured are 05 women. (a)"
